### Item2Vec API 测试请求

# 基础URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

### 1. 健康检查
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 2. 第一次训练模型
POST {{baseUrl}}/train
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "data": [
        "apple orange banana",
        "apple computer laptop", 
        "orange juice drink",
        "banana fruit healthy",
        "computer technology modern"
    ]
}

###

### 3. 第二次训练（渐进训练）
POST {{baseUrl}}/train
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "data": [
        "laptop portable computer",
        "juice beverage liquid",
        "drink beverage refreshment", 
        "fruit healthy nutrition",
        "technology modern innovation",
        "new item smartphone",
        "smartphone mobile device"
    ]
}

###

### 4. 生成向量 - 已知词汇
POST {{baseUrl}}/gen_vec
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "item": "apple"
}

###

### 5. 生成向量 - 新增词汇
POST {{baseUrl}}/gen_vec
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "item": "smartphone"
}

###

### 6. 生成向量 - 未知词汇
POST {{baseUrl}}/gen_vec
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "item": "unknown_word"
}

###

### 7. 生成向量 - 多个测试
